{"id": "ChIJrw8HXQDbwoARj3T7MS-97h4", "rating": 4.7, "userRatingCount": 371, "displayName": {"text": "Molly Tea (Arcadia)", "languageCode": "en"}, "reviews": [{"name": "places/ChIJrw8HXQDbwoARj3T7MS-97h4/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT25kZlN6TnFiVXBXVlRGT01YcEVTbmhMZUVsRE5uYxAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "4 months ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "I always order 100% sugar, no ice — their 70% sweetness is a bit light, and full sweetness brings out the tea flavor best.\n\nMy Favorite Drinks\n\n• Premium Jasmine Milk Tea – 9.5/10\nAromatic, smooth, consistently the best.\n• White Champaca Milk Tea – 9.0/10\nElegant floral aroma with a velvety finish.\n• White Champaca Oolong Milk Tea – 9.0/10\nRoasted oolong depth balances the champaca sweetness.\n• Camellia Oolong Milk Tea – 9.0/10\nFragrant, deep, and well‑rounded.\n• Osmanthus Milk Tea – 8.5/10\nLight, delicate, slightly apricot‑scented.\n• White Champaca Matcha Milk Tea – 8.0/10\nEarthy matcha + bright champaca; more of an acquired taste.\n\nConsistent drinks, clean shop, fast service. Great spot if you love floral, premium tea bases.", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "I always order 100% sugar, no ice — their 70% sweetness is a bit light, and full sweetness brings out the tea flavor best.\n\nMy Favorite Drinks\n\n• Premium Jasmine Milk Tea – 9.5/10\nAromatic, smooth, consistently the best.\n• White Champaca Milk Tea – 9.0/10\nElegant floral aroma with a velvety finish.\n• White Champaca Oolong Milk Tea – 9.0/10\nRoasted oolong depth balances the champaca sweetness.\n• Camellia Oolong Milk Tea – 9.0/10\nFragrant, deep, and well‑rounded.\n• Osmanthus Milk Tea – 8.5/10\nLight, delicate, slightly apricot‑scented.\n• White Champaca Matcha Milk Tea – 8.0/10\nEarthy matcha + bright champaca; more of an acquired taste.\n\nConsistent drinks, clean shop, fast service. Great spot if you love floral, premium tea bases.", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Mia Ly", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/113428912477601945065/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWauFMH99RZ2wiyHnUUkLiL5WrXpH1zyZKCcmfJaBgM_oZhjH9Ekg=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba6"}, "publishTime": "2026-02-18T05:06:44.272635197Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT25kZlN6TnFiVXBXVlRGT01YcEVTbmhMZUVsRE5uYxAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT25kZlN6TnFiVXBXVlRGT01YcEVTbmhMZUVsRE5uYxAB!2m1!1s0x80c2db005d070faf:0x1eeebd2f31fb748f"}, {"name": "places/ChIJrw8HXQDbwoARj3T7MS-97h4/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2tRNVMwUm5TMDVuT0dwa1ZqbEVUVkZrYTA1ZloxRRAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "3 weeks ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "Had a great experience at Molly Tea! The drinks were fresh, flavorful, and perfectly balanced—not too sweet and very refreshing. The quality of the ingredients really stands out, and the presentation was beautiful as well. The staff were friendly, welcoming, and helpful with recommendations. The store was clean, cozy, and had a great atmosphere. Definitely one of the best tea spots in the area. I’ll be coming back and recommending it to friends!", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "Had a great experience at Molly Tea! The drinks were fresh, flavorful, and perfectly balanced—not too sweet and very refreshing. The quality of the ingredients really stands out, and the presentation was beautiful as well. The staff were friendly, welcoming, and helpful with recommendations. The store was clean, cozy, and had a great atmosphere. Definitely one of the best tea spots in the area. I’ll be coming back and recommending it to friends!", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Haolin Li", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/117283341557991880427/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocI164c2rEglXrCECdsf0JlX6tMV3d9jzi1GKLSAFQeseb6eGA=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo"}, "publishTime": "2026-06-16T23:34:33.461460413Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2tRNVMwUm5TMDVuT0dwa1ZqbEVUVkZrYTA1ZloxRRAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2tRNVMwUm5TMDVuT0dwa1ZqbEVUVkZrYTA1ZloxRRAB!2m1!1s0x80c2db005d070faf:0x1eeebd2f31fb748f"}, {"name": "places/ChIJrw8HXQDbwoARj3T7MS-97h4/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT205T2JFZzNZMW80WkVSTVpucGpRMmhTWjJJeU5sRRAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "5 months ago", "rating": 4, "text": {"text": "Visited twice during their soft opening, but found the wait times to be highly unpredictable (5 minutes for my first visit and over 40 minutes for the second). Regarding the menu, while the staff recommends 70% sugar, I found very little difference between the 50% and 30% sweetness levels. The current ambiance is quite hectic, with more people standing around waiting than actually relaxing. If you're looking for a spot to chill rather than just grab a quick drink, you might want to look elsewhere for now.", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "Visited twice during their soft opening, but found the wait times to be highly unpredictable (5 minutes for my first visit and over 40 minutes for the second). Regarding the menu, while the staff recommends 70% sugar, I found very little difference between the 50% and 30% sweetness levels. The current ambiance is quite hectic, with more people standing around waiting than actually relaxing. If you're looking for a spot to chill rather than just grab a quick drink, you might want to look elsewhere for now.", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Emi", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/110154151247659970565/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjW_gyhiy04x9Ocf83Fmuk6Do73TMQJ16TyYYmkUm2Gsc8hA9_LNAA=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba4"}, "publishTime": "2026-01-31T18:34:08.054774049Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT205T2JFZzNZMW80WkVSTVpucGpRMmhTWjJJeU5sRRAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT205T2JFZzNZMW80WkVSTVpucGpRMmhTWjJJeU5sRRAB!2m1!1s0x80c2db005d070faf:0x1eeebd2f31fb748f"}, {"name": "places/ChIJrw8HXQDbwoARj3T7MS-97h4/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT21ONVRrVmlTM1p0YTNsVVdHVk1hMVJQYkVSVE0yYxAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "2 months ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "Molly Tea is absolutely amazing! The tea is fresh, flavorful, and perfectly balanced every time. The staff are friendly and welcoming, and the shop has such a cozy, relaxing vibe. I especially loved the creamy milk tea and the quality ingredients really stand out. Fast service, beautiful presentation, and consistently delicious drinks — definitely one of my favorite tea spots. Highly recommend!", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "Molly Tea is absolutely amazing! The tea is fresh, flavorful, and perfectly balanced every time. The staff are friendly and welcoming, and the shop has such a cozy, relaxing vibe. I especially loved the creamy milk tea and the quality ingredients really stand out. Fast service, beautiful presentation, and consistently delicious drinks — definitely one of my favorite tea spots. Highly recommend!", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Ban_Bun", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/100642463988922872766/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVibSDiKOIhTFqRnLwU0W7BKN81v_DFnLjf_zJb_7U41CibhAk=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo"}, "publishTime": "2026-05-07T02:55:34.181087538Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT21ONVRrVmlTM1p0YTNsVVdHVk1hMVJQYkVSVE0yYxAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT21ONVRrVmlTM1p0YTNsVVdHVk1hMVJQYkVSVE0yYxAB!2m1!1s0x80c2db005d070faf:0x1eeebd2f31fb748f"}, {"name": "places/ChIJrw8HXQDbwoARj3T7MS-97h4/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT20xNWEwVjBXVk5XV0hGNmFVSkxlRXQzYm1OaFNsRRAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "2 months ago", "rating": 4, "text": {"text": "Took advantage of the BOGO special for Tongmu Lapsang Bubble Tea. This boba tea joint lives up to the hype. The boba pearls are chewy / qq. This chain uses premium exotic tea leaves from China, targeting Gen Z demographics. Each order is freshly prepared, the wait time is around 5 minutes depending how busy it is. The taste of the tea and brown sugar is well balanced with 30% sugar level and regular ice. Would return to try other offerings.", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "Took advantage of the BOGO special for Tongmu Lapsang Bubble Tea. This boba tea joint lives up to the hype. The boba pearls are chewy / qq. This chain uses premium exotic tea leaves from China, targeting Gen Z demographics. Each order is freshly prepared, the wait time is around 5 minutes depending how busy it is. The taste of the tea and brown sugar is well balanced with 30% sugar level and regular ice. Would return to try other offerings.", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Carl Wong", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/106521176213250283556/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWzzzCEbFywrfN6J8D1cg9gzfF5k6W__avTERzLSOylhZ2b_2N4=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba6"}, "publishTime": "2026-04-20T18:43:20.015453179Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT20xNWEwVjBXVk5XV0hGNmFVSkxlRXQzYm1OaFNsRRAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT20xNWEwVjBXVk5XV0hGNmFVSkxlRXQzYm1OaFNsRRAB!2m1!1s0x80c2db005d070faf:0x1eeebd2f31